Forever Young;;1992;;PG;;Drama,Romance,Sci-Fi;;6.3;;Steve Miner;;Mel Gibson,Jamie Lee Curtis,Elijah Wood,Isabel Glasser,George Wendt,Joe Morton,Nicolas Surovy,David Marshall Grant,Robert Hy Gorman,Millie Slavin,Michael A. Goorjian,Veronica Lauren,Art LaFleur,Eric Pierpoint,Walton Goggins,Amanda Foreman,Karla Tamburrelli,Robert Munns;;A 1939 test pilot asks his best friend to use him as a guinea pig for a cryogenics experiment. Daniel McCormick wants to be frozen for a year so that he doesn't have to watch his love lying in a coma. The next thing Daniel knows is that he's been awoken in 1992.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0104291/